@@yVerdict@@W                                              Sentinel level 20

Syntax: verdict

Consume all accumulated testimony marks and deliver a single melee strike
whose damage and secondary effect scale with marks spent.

@@yVerdict Tiers:@@W
  @@w1-2 marks@@W: @@yRebuke@@W     — 1.5x damage, no secondary effect.
  @@w3-4 marks@@W: @@yCensure@@W    — 2.5x damage, target -2 hitroll (3 rds).
  @@w5-6 marks@@W: @@yBinding@@W    — 4x damage, target speed debuff (4 rds).
  @@w7-8 marks@@W: @@ySealing@@W    — 6x damage, target silenced (2 rds).
  @@w9 marks@@W:   @@RFINAL@@W      — 9x damage, target stunned (1 rd).

All verdicts gain a WIS-scaled damage bonus. Higher tiers include all lower
tier effects.

After spending marks, testimony accumulation pauses for 2 rounds.

No mana cost — the verdict is powered by observation, not magic.

See also: @@mtestimony sentinel condemn@@W
